---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SideNav from '../components/SideNav.astro';
import Lightbox from '../components/Lightbox.astro';
import NextProject from '../components/NextProject.astro';
import siteConfig from '../content/site-config.json';

const { projects } = siteConfig;
const project = projects.metalEden;

const sections = [
  { id: 'overview', label: 'Overview' },
  { id: 'about-project', label: 'About' },
  { id: 'responsibilities', label: 'Responsibilities' },
  { id: 'environments', label: 'Environments' },
  { id: 'weapons', label: 'Weapons' },
  { id: 'props', label: '3D Art' },
  { id: 'collaboration', label: 'Collaboration' },
  { id: 'optimization', label: 'Optimization' },
];
---

<BaseLayout title={project.title} description={`Case study for ${project.title} - ${project.roles.join(', ')}`}>
  <SideNav sections={sections} />
  <Lightbox />

  <main class="snap-container snap-disabled">
    <!-- Section 1: Overview / Hero -->
    <section id="overview" class="snap-section section-hero">
      <div class="section-bg">
        <img src="/images/metal-eden/hero-main.webp" alt="METAL EDEN overview" loading="eager" width="3840" height="1600" />
      </div>
      <div class="section-overlay"></div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h1>{project.title}</h1>
        <p class="project-roles">Associate Art Director | Lead & Senior Artist</p>
        <p class="project-specialization">Environment, Weapons & 3D</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: About the Project -->
    <section id="about-project" class="snap-section section-about-project">
      <div class="about-project-content">
        <div class="about-project-text" data-reveal>
          <h2>About the Project</h2>
          <p>
            METAL EDEN is a AA sci-fi FPS developed by Reikon Games in Unreal Engine 5, requiring strong visual readability and cohesion across dense, high-velocity combat spaces.
          </p>
          <p>
            The art direction drew from Akira, Ghost in the Shell, and Metal Gear Solid, shaping those influences into a cohesive, fresh visual language.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.deepsilver.com/games/metal-eden" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-link">Visit Metal Eden Site ↗</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-project-stats" data-reveal-stagger>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-value" data-count-to="3" data-count-suffix="+ Years">3+ Years</span>
            <span class="stat-label">In Production</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-value" data-count-to="120" data-count-suffix="+ Developers">120+ Developers</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Total Team Size</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-value" data-count-to="30" data-count-suffix="+ Artists">30+ Artists</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Art Team</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-value">Engine</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Unreal Engine 5</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Responsibilities & Leadership -->
    <section id="responsibilities" class="snap-section section-split">
      <div class="split-content">
        <div class="split-text" data-reveal>
          <h2>My Responsibilities & Scope</h2>
          <ul class="responsibility-list" data-reveal-stagger>
            <li><strong>Co-defined and maintained</strong> the game's <strong>visual identity</strong>, ensuring stylistic consistency across a <strong>team of 30+ artists</strong>.</li>
            <li>Personally responsible for <strong>level art production</strong> from <strong>blockout through final polish</strong> across multiple maps.</li>
            <li>Defined and owned the <strong>weapon production pipeline</strong>, personally delivering weapon assets and <strong>leading the weapons team</strong>.</li>
            <li>Defined the <strong>hard-surface visual direction</strong>, collaborated with the tech team to build the <strong>production pipeline</strong>, and delivered assets from <strong>concept to final in-game models</strong>.</li>
            <li><strong>Drove and personally executed</strong> performance <strong>optimization</strong> across all maps and content for target platforms.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="split-video">
          <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
            <source src="/images/metal-eden/responsibilities-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section: Challenges -->
    <section class="snap-section section-challenges">
      <div class="challenges-content" data-reveal>
        <h2>Challenges</h2>
        <p>One of the main challenges was <strong>rapidly scaling the team from around 30 to over 120 developers</strong> during active production. This introduced pipeline, communication, and coordination challenges that required <strong>constant iteration and refinement of workflows</strong> to keep production efficient and aligned.</p>
        <p>Another key challenge was the project's highly specific <strong>industrial hard-surface sci-fi art style</strong>, which is relatively uncommon. Finding artists already fluent in this visual language was difficult, so a major focus was on <strong>guiding artists into the style</strong>, establishing clear standards, and designing workflows that reduced friction and inconsistency while maintaining <strong>visual coherence</strong> across the project.</p>
        <p>Finally, <strong>performance was a critical concern</strong>. The game featured dense geometry, large numbers of assets on screen, and very fast player movement, requiring <strong>aggressive environment and level optimization</strong>, particularly for consoles and lower-end PCs. This demanded close collaboration and careful trade-offs to achieve visual quality while meeting performance targets.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contributions Header -->
    <section class="contributions-header" data-reveal>
      <h2>My Contributions</h2>
      <p class="contributions-subtitle">The following sections describe my contributions to the project. All presented work was created or led by me.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Environments & Level Art -->
    <section id="environments" class="snap-section section-environments">
      <div class="env-content" data-reveal>
        <h2>Level and Environment Art</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Delivered level art production from <strong>blockout to final polish across multiple maps</strong>. Responsible for the <strong>overall visual pass</strong>, including composition, mood, and set dressing. Every decision was driven by gameplay, while guiding the team through consistent feedback.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="env-hero-image" data-reveal>
        <div class="image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/env-hero.webp" alt="METAL EDEN environment" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1600" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Level Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Composition, lighting, mood, color and final detail pass.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="env-image-row" data-reveal-stagger>
        <div class="env-image-half image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/env-left.webp" alt="METAL EDEN environment" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1600" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Level Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Composition, lighting, mood, color and final detail pass.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="env-image-half image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/env-right.webp" alt="METAL EDEN environment" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1600" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Level Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Composition, lighting, mood, color and final detail pass.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="env-archive-link">
        <a href="https://www.artstation.com/kiko_main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Full Environment and Level Art available on ArtStation →
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="inline-cta" data-reveal>
        <span>Interested in working together?</span>
        <a href="/contact">Get in Touch →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 4: Weapons -->
    <section id="weapons" class="snap-section section-environments">
      <div class="env-content" data-reveal>
        <h2>Weapon Art</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Personally created weapon assets, established the weapon production pipeline with the tech team, and led the weapons art team.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="env-hero-video">
        <div class="image-attributed">
          <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
            <source src="/images/metal-eden/weapons-hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Weapon & FPP Arms</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Full mid-poly in-game model for weapon and FPP arms, from blockout to textures.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="env-archive-link">
        <a href="https://www.artstation.com/kiko_main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Full Weapons Art available on ArtStation →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 5: Props & Modular Kits -->
    <section id="props" class="snap-section section-environments">
      <div class="env-content" data-reveal>
        <h2>3D Art</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          Establish the hard-surface 3D visual direction, delivering assets from concept through final in-game models while establishing the production pipeline with the tech team.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="env-hero-image" data-reveal>
        <div class="image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/props-hero.webp" alt="METAL EDEN props" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1845" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Concept and 3D Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Fully created assets from concept to 3D in-game model.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="env-image-row" data-reveal-stagger>
        <div class="env-image-half image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/props-left.webp" alt="METAL EDEN props" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1845" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Concept and 3D Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Fully created assets from concept to 3D in-game model.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="env-image-half image-attributed">
          <img src="/images/metal-eden/props-right.webp" alt="METAL EDEN props" loading="lazy" class="zoomable" width="3840" height="1845" />
          <div class="attribution-badge">
            <span class="attribution-title">Concept and 3D Art</span>
            <span class="attribution-desc">Fully created assets from concept to 3D in-game model.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="env-archive-link">
        <a href="https://www.artstation.com/kiko_main" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          More props and Concept Art available on ArtStation →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 6: Collaboration & Leadership -->
    <section id="collaboration" class="snap-section section-environments section-compact">
      <div class="env-content" data-reveal>
        <h2>Collaboration & Leadership</h2>
        <ul class="collaboration-list" data-reveal-stagger>
          <li>Provided <strong>constant visual feedback</strong> and guidance to maintain <strong>quality and consistency</strong> across the art team</li>
          <li><strong>Collaborated closely with gameplay and tech teams</strong> to align visual direction with gameplay and performance targets</li>
          <li>Balanced <strong>hands-on production</strong> with broader <strong>leadership responsibilities</strong></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 7: Optimization -->
    <section id="optimization" class="snap-section section-optimization">
      <div class="section-content">
        <h2 data-reveal>Optimization</h2>
        <p class="section-intro" data-reveal>
          Visual quality and optimization are treated as <strong>inseparable</strong> throughout my production workflow.
        </p>
        <div class="optimization-grid" data-reveal-stagger>
          <div class="optimization-card">
            <p><strong>Implemented aggressive level streaming strategies</strong> to support large, model heavy environments</p>
          </div>
          <div class="optimization-card">
            <p>Use of <strong>shader-driven materials</strong> to reduce texture memory and draw calls</p>
          </div>
          <div class="optimization-card">
            <p><strong>Environment kitbashing</strong> in engine to maximize asset reuse</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Accolades -->
    <section class="accolades-section">
      <div class="accolades-bg">
        <img src="/images/metal-eden/accolades-bg.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" width="1920" height="1080" />
      </div>
      <div class="accolades-overlay"></div>
      <h2 class="accolades-title" data-reveal>METAL EDEN</h2>
      <div class="accolades-content" data-reveal-stagger>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Visually impressive."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">TechRadar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Absolutely gorgeous to look at."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">TechRadar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Dazzling presentation."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">Niche Gamer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Looks amazing."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">Niche Gamer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Impressive visuals and art direction."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">Niche Gamer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"A lot to appreciate about the art direction."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">GamingBolt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Genuinely stunning vibe."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">GamingBolt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Enemy and gun designs stand out."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">VGChartz</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"The art team deserves full praise."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">G Style Magazine</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"Environments drip with detail."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">G Style Magazine</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accolade">
          <p class="accolade-quote">"One of the better looking games this year."</p>
          <span class="accolade-source">DLH.net</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inline-cta inline-cta--light" data-reveal>
        <span>Interested in working together?</span>
        <a href="/contact">Get in Touch →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="gallery-cta" data-reveal>
      <p class="gallery-cta-text">Want to see more?</p>
      <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-primary">View Full Gallery</a>
    </section>

    <NextProject
      title="RUINER 2 - Vertical Slice"
      href="/ruiner-2"
      image="/images/ruiner-2/hero-bg.webp"
    />

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Snap Container */
  .snap-container {
    height: 100vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
  }

  .snap-container.snap-disabled {
    scroll-snap-type: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .snap-container {
      scroll-snap-type: none;
      height: auto;
      overflow-y: visible;
    }
  }

  /* Snap Sections */
  .snap-section {
    min-height: 100vh;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    scroll-snap-stop: always;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    padding-top: calc(64px + var(--spacing-lg));
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .snap-section {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--spacing-md));
    }
  }

  /* Section Hero */
  .section-hero {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -2;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    animation: kenBurns 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes kenBurns {
    0% { transform: scale(1); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.08); }
  }

  @keyframes heroFadeIn {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .section-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(14, 15, 17, 0.6) 0%,
      rgba(14, 15, 17, 0.35) 50%,
      rgba(14, 15, 17, 0.8) 100%
    );
  }

  .section-content {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .section-hero h1 {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFadeIn 0.8s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
  }

  .project-roles {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFadeIn 0.8s ease-out 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .project-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .section-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .project-roles {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .project-specialization {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-top: -6px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: heroFadeIn 0.8s ease-out 0.7s forwards;
  }

  /* Section About Project */
  .section-about-project {
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
    min-height: auto;
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .about-project-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-project-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .about-project-text p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
  }

  .about-project-text p + p {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .project-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .project-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-project-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-project-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .about-project-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-md);
      width: 100%;
    }

    .stat-item {
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  /* Section Split */
  .section-split {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    min-height: auto;
    padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .contributions-header {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    text-align: left;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .contributions-header h2 {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .contributions-subtitle {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    width: 100%;
    margin: var(--spacing-sm) auto 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .split-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .split-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .responsibility-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .responsibility-list li {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
    position: relative;
  }

  .responsibility-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 8px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .split-image {
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .split-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .split-video {
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .split-video video {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .split-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .split-image {
      order: -1;
    }
  }

  /* Section Gallery */
  .section-gallery {
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .gallery-placeholder {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .gallery-placeholder p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .placeholder-note {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .section-details h3 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .section-details ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .section-details li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-details li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Section Environments */
  .section-environments {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
